  "texts": [
    "As shown in Fig. 6, our stakeholders represented a broad range of senior digital health stakeholders.",
    "Stage III: participant co-creation After participants agreed to participate and submitted a consent form, they were introduced to the mind map by the moderator (CL) during recorded video calls.",
    "The moderator asked each stakeholder to comment on the prompts in each thematic area of the Mural board.",
    "Each stakeholder was granted access to the Mural board after the moderated session, with the possibility of further editing the mind map by posting additional notes or by commenting on other participants' notes.",
    "46 stakeholders posted, edited, and discussed our digital mindmap hosted on the web-based platform MURAL.com from December 2021 until April 2022."
  ],
